---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy — LuckyToss"
	description="LuckyToss privacy policy: all coin flips and dice rolls happen locally in your browser, no data is uploaded or stored."
	canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
		<h1 class="font-[Sora] text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#221b10] sm:text-4xl">
			Privacy Policy
		</h1>
		<div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-[#4a4234]">
			<p>
				LuckyToss runs entirely on your own device, inside your browser. No
				roll, flip, streak, or history is ever uploaded to, or stored on, any
				server operated by LuckyToss. Closing or refreshing the tab clears
				all session data.
			</p>
			<p>
				LuckyToss uses standard web analytics to understand aggregate traffic
				(page views, referrers) and may display advertising through Google
				AdSense, which can set its own cookies subject to Google's own
				privacy policy.
			</p>
			<p>
				If you have questions about this policy, contact us via the details
				on the About page.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
